  "chapters": [
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch26",
      "text": "So, Alex, first question—what’s the most unexpected thing you’ve ever done?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch27",
      "text": "Unexpected? You mean like running into an old acquaintance and letting them buy me a drink?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch28",
      "text": "Touché. But I was thinking something a little riskier.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch29",
      "text": "Risky, huh? Well… once, I jumped into a stranger’s convertible just for the thrill of the ride.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch30",
      "text": "That’s bold. And here I thought I was the adventurous one.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch31",
      "text": "Your turn. What’s the most reckless thing you’ve done?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch32",
      "text": "Hmm… once I bet everything I had on a single poker hand. Let’s just say, I got lucky.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch33",
      "text": "A gambler, huh? Should I be worried?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch34",
      "text": "Only if you don’t like taking chances.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch35",
      "text": "I take my chances when they’re worth it.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch36",
      "text": "And what about tonight, Alex? Feeling lucky?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch37",
      "text": "Ask me after another drink.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch38",
      "text": "Now that sounds like a challenge I can’t resist.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch39",
      "text": "I bet you can’t. But let’s make it interesting—loser of the next game picks up the tab.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch40",
      "text": "Deal. But I should warn you—I never lose.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch41",
      "text": "We’ll see about that, Bob.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch42",
      "text": "Alright, pick a game. But choose wisely, because I don’t intend to go easy on you.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch43",
      "text": "How about a coin toss? Simple, fair, and leaves it all to fate.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch44",
      "text": "You trust fate that much?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch45",
      "text": "Sometimes. But mostly, I just like to see if people are willing to take a leap.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch46",
      "text": "Alright, I’m in. Call it—heads or tails?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch47",
      "text": "Heads. Let’s see if luck is on my side tonight.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch48",
      "text": "Let’s find out, Alex.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    }
